            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked through, transfer the <strong>chicken</strong> to a clean board and shred it apart, using two forks - this technique is known as ‘pulling’</p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach </strong>and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
