    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>hearty chicken & spelt soup</strong> and drizzle over the <strong>parsley oil</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>ciabatta toasts </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
